    Darkosparko's shrine to Pixar's Cars is a fascinating example of sticking to
    a design that fits the purpose. This page has checkered flags baked into the
    frames and Lightning's candy red paint color everywhere. It would be really
    fun to pick a favorite movie of my own and theme a shrine to it.
